reviewText: Yet another "wild ride" from all the "Ladies" of WEW, Includes matches from all the WEW stars like, Alexis Laree(Mickie James), Jazz, Amy Lee, Annie Social, Talia Madison(Velvet Sky), April Hunter and many, many more. All this plus it comes with an Annie Social mini poster, who could want more?
I can't find anything bad to say about this dvd set. More of the same great female wrestling that WEW fans have come to expect.
